query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_prices,
  COUNT(DISTINCT serviceId) as unique_services,
  COUNT(DISTINCT countryId) as unique_countries,
  COUNT(DISTINCT apiId) as unique_apis
FROM prices;
